title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan and Special Guest Amy!
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan and Special Guest Amy!
description:
Morgan and Amy break down all of the best segments on the show this week. Amy shares the entire backstory of her connection to George Strait, they discuss the awkwardness of one of the segments that happened this week + they dive deep into some big life moments.
